Package: weathergrib
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, weathergrib-maps, fonts-liberation
Description: Weathergrib is a Grib file reader and visualizes meteorological data 
 Weathergrib is a Grib file reader and visualizes meteorological data providing an off-line capability to analyse weather forecasts or hindcasts. The Weathergrib software is released as open source under the GPLv3 License.

Package: weathergrib-maps
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:depends}
Description: Maps for Weathergrib weather visualisation
 This contains maps and country names used by Weathergrib
